Material and distribution. Holotype examined, deposited in the Zoölogisch Museum Amsterdam ( ZMA –
POR 11322
), collected at Jamaica , Discovery Bay, LTS, 51.8 m in depth. Material examined here includes specimens from (but is not restricted to) the Bahamas (INV– POR 932 ), Barbados (INV– POR 911, 917 ), Curaçao (INV– POR 901, 907, 910 ), Venezuela (Morrocoy, INV– POR 1196 ), Jamaica (INV– POR 1000, 1011) and San Andrés Island (INV– POR 986 ).
